-@{lindent 13} New features were implemented:
The sorting of files by name, date or size, and the sorting of directories.
The regulation of list lines width.
The control at width of diz-text.
Autosearch for extractor if its full path is not specified in the line @{" Command " Link "EDIT_COMMAND"}.
Improved layout of the text in list.
@{lindent 1}
version 1.03 @{fg highlight}(13.09.96)@{fg text}@{lindent 11}
-@{lindent 13} Previous versions do not start if settings load is fault or if filetypes file not found. This is corrected.
Now all program messages is printed under locale.
The program did not work correctly in @{b}Current Mode@{ub}. This bug is fixed.
Construction of the line @{" Command " Link "EDIT_COMMAND"} is amended.
Stack overflow problem is fixed.
The full revision of sources is made for speed up of program and for code length minimization.
@{lindent 1}
version 1.02 @{fg highlight}(17.08.96)@{fg text}@{lindent 11}
