@Node "WORD_DECLENSION" "The word declension."
@{jcenter}
The word declension.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
@{jleft}@{lindent 1}    First of all I thank to Dmitry Mikhilov for elaboration the rusgrammar.library and the program for russian language support called "Rusifier". The declension of russian words is made by this software.

   What is the problem? In some languages (including russian) the plural noun has variforms of ending depended with number. For example in english we write 2 files, 5 files, 21 files etc. As You see the word "files" is not changed. But in russian it is not like this because the word "file" is wrote different with these numbers. It is not easy for control at number and correct the ending of nouns everywhere. This problem was solved for Russia by programmer Dmitry Mikhvilov. He made the special library and the program Rusifier which use one. Now program ListDIZ use these features.

   For programmers: The new assembly function was implemented in program ListDIZ. This function is replacement for function @{b}sprintf()@{ub}. Now formated print to a string is emulated with call the function @{b}RawDoFmt()@{ub} for "critical" lines. If the program for language support is used in your country and one patch the function @{b}RawDoFmt()@{ub} then You can correct locale messages for "critical" lines wich special signs for your patch function. If You have interested then please apply to documentation of rusgrammar.library and ©Rusifier for details.

@EndNode

@Node "CONCEPT" "What is this for ?"
@{jcenter}
Description and sphere of employment.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
@{jleft}@{lindent 1}    First of all this software was wrote especially for men who have to do with archives often and often, thus for sysops and BBSes users.

   There is good rule that place in every archive inquiry file named "File_id.diz" with short information about contents of archive. An archive without this file has very good chance to be moved in trash.

   There are more types of archives and if You have to do with ones then You is in need of suitable programs which search and extract inquiry files from archives. If it is true then program ListDIZ for You! This software try to unite all diz_texts extractors under the command of You. Program ListDIZ give You very comfortable interface for control of the extract process from any types of archives.

   It is fact that already there is software which try to make it work. Well, but program ListDIZ is neither arexx script nor CLI utility, it is full Workbench-compatible program. Try use ListDIZ and make your choice.

   Program ListDIZ is:
-@{lindent 3} beautiful user interface based on @{" MUI " Link "MUI"};@{lindent 1}
-@{lindent 3} identification ANY types of archives with three factors: filename suffix, hex-contents, or with datatypes method, and with combinations of them;@{lindent 1}
-@{lindent 3} flexible management of extractors, that make possible to easy exchange old extractors with new ones or with others;@{lindent 1}
-@{lindent 3} great possibilities for configuration of program and builtin functions (up to full automatization of all processes);@{lindent 1}
- and more others...

@EndNode

@Node "REQUIREMENT" "What is program need for run ?"
@{jcenter}
Program requirement.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
@{jleft}@{lindent 1}    First of all the program ListDIZ uses @{" MUI " Link "MUI"} and You must have it with version 3.5 at least.

   In additional You must have OS 3.0+ and next libraries:
- dos.library       v36+;
- intuition.library v36+;
- locale.library    v38+;
- datatypes.library v39+;
- reqtools.library  v38+ (included in distribution kit);
- expname.library   v2+  (included in distribution kit).

   In this moment program ListDIZ is compiled for usage with 68020 processor. If You wish the optimized version for any others then contact with @{" author " Link "ADDRESS"}.

@EndNode

@Node "INSTALL" "How do install the program ListDIZ ?"
@{jcenter}
Program installation.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
@{jleft}@{lindent 1}    It is not hard. Create individual directory (ex. @{b}SYS:MY_PROGS/ListDIZ@{ub}) and copy into one all files & directories from distribution kit. If You run program first time then I recommend copy contents of directory @{b}env@{ub} in your system directories @{b}ENV:@{ub} and @{b}ENVARC:@{ub}. It make easy window gadgets layout and fix windows size & position and others parameters of @{" MUI " Link "MUI"}.

   If after program start You receive program message about lack of some library then copy one from directory @{b}libs@{ub} in your system directory @{b}LIBS:@{ub}.

   About how do further use please read chapter @{" Usage " Link "USAGE"}.
@EndNode

@Node "USAGE" "How do use program ListDIZ ?"
@{jcenter}
Program usage.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
@{jleft}@{lindent 1}    Before usage with program, it need to be installed. About how do install the program please read chapter @{" Installation " Link "INSTALL"}.

   After installation program, it ready to use. I strongly recommend to read chapter @{" Responsibility " Link "WARRANTY"} before start usage.

   Usage of program ListDIZ as any good program is very easy. Before full usage description it will be observed that Main control window has some gadgets and buttons for program control.

   Working algorithm is easy. You select files and/or directories which will be scaned, then select destination file in which will be stored ready list of extracted diz_files. After that You press "Start" button. It is all.

   However ListDIZ has powerful interface and more features. Following I descript ones.

   So, program ListDIZ has five windows:
@{jcenter}
@{" Main control window       " Link "MAIN_WIN"}
@{" Settings control window   " Link "SETS_WIN"}
@{" Progress indicator window " Link "INDI_WIN"}
@{" Diz_text window           " Link "SHOW_WIN"}
@{" Registration window       " Link "REGI_WIN"}

@EndNode

